ench\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1317, \"end\": 1333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999996220299895, \"rank\": 2.597642887712772e-07, \"text\": \"Paralympic Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1365, \"end\": 1375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3209974138860086e-15, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Amnesty's women's rights researcher\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1231}, {\"ngram\": \"sports hijabs\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1297}, {\"ngram\": \"a mockery\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"claims\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1359}, {\"ngram\": \"the first \\\"Gender Equal Olympics\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France does not ban hijabs in public spaces.\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1459, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1415, \"end\": 1421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999815433468716, \"rank\": 1.8045001202915305e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hijabs\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1441}, {\"ngram\": \"public spaces\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But its policies on the headscarf can be confusing.\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1511, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its policies\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1476}, {\"ngram\": \"the headscarf\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A law passed in 2010 prohibits the wearing of any face-covering headgear.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1586, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A law\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"the wearing\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1555}, {\"ngram\": \"any face-covering headgear\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This included masks, balaclavas, niq\\u0101bs and other veils covering the face.\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1662, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"masks\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1607}, {\"ngram\": \"balaclavas\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1619}, {\"ngram\": \"niq\\u0101bs\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1627}, {\"ngram\": \"other veils\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1643}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But because the hijab does not cover a person's face, it is allowed.\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1731, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hijab\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1684}, {\"ngram\": \"a person's face\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2023, France also decided to ban public school students from wearing the abaya - a long dress or robe popular among women in certain Muslim cultures 'It lays bare the racist gender discrimination that underpins access to sport in the country.'\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1980, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1742, \"end\": 1748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999815433468716, \"rank\": 1.8045001202915305e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1869, \"end\": 1875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.9687098981136054, \"rank\": 0.03230079711826201, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"public school students\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1791}, {\"ngram\": \"the abaya\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1814}, {\"ngram\": \"a long dress\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1829}, {\"ngram\": \"robe\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1837}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1857}, {\"ngram\": \"the racist gender discrimination\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1931}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 1953}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1962}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1977}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: 'Discriminatory rules policing what women wear are a violation of Muslim women's and girls' human rights and have a devastating impact on their participation in sport, blocking efforts to make sports more inclusive and more accessible.'\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 2229, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2059, \"end\": 2065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.9687098981136054, \"rank\": 0.03230079711826201, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Discriminatory rules\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2014}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2034}, {\"ngram\": \"a violation\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2055}, {\"ngram\": \"a devastating impact\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2127}, {\"ngram\": \"their participation\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2150}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2159}, {\"ngram\": \"efforts\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French sports minister Amelie Oudea-Castera barred French athletes from wearing the hijab, saying they are bound by the country's strict separation of religion and state.\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2231, \"end\": 2237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.6950629566232579, \"rank\": 0.4293890195700075, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Amelie Oudea-Castera\", \"from\": 2254, \"to\": 2274}, {\"ngram\": \"the hijab\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2320}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's strict separation\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2378}, {\"ngram\": \"religion\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2390}, {\"ngram\": \"state\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'What does that mean?\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2424, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That means a ban on any type of proselytising,' she told French TV.\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2492, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2482, \"end\": 2488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.6950629566232579, \"rank\": 0.4293890195700075, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a ban\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2441}, {\"ngram\": \"any type\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2453}, {\"ngram\": \"proselytising\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'That means absolute neutrality in public services, the French team will not wear the headscarf.'\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2550, \"end\": 2556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.6950629566232579, \"rank\": 0.4293890195700075, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"absolute neutrality\", \"from\": 2506, \"to\": 2525}, {\"ngram\": \"public services\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2544}, {\"ngram\": \"the headscarf\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Proselytising is the act of attempting to change people's religious or political beliefs.\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2682, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Proselytising\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2606}, {\"ngram\": \"the act\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2617}, {\"ngram\": \"people's religious or political beliefs\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2681}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The values of Olympism are excellence, respect and friendship.\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2746, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The values\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympism\", \"from\": 2698, \"to\": 2706}, {\"ngram\": \"excellence\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2721}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 2723, \"to\": 2730}, {\"ngram\": \"friendship\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The host country above all should honour these.\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2794, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The host country\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But#Franceis the only country in Europe that specifically bans sport hijabs#ParisOlympics2024#Paris2024\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0091\\u0087https://t.co/u0o2sNFtBepic.twitter.com/mjqsXlebtF In France, the prohibition on Muslim women from wearing any form of religious headgear extends far beyond the Olympic and Paralympic Games.\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 3092, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2956, \"end\": 2962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999815433468716, \"rank\": 1.8045001202915305e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2983, \"end\": 2989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.9687098981136054, \"rank\": 0.03230079711826201, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only country\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2824}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 2828, \"to\": 2834}, {\"ngram\": \"sport hijabs#ParisOlympics2024#Paris2024\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0091\\u0087https://t.co/u0o2sNFtBepic.twitter.com/mjqsXlebtF\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2951}, {\"ngram\": \"the prohibition\", \"from\": 2963, \"to\": 2978}, {\"ngram\": \"any form\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3016}, {\"ngram\": \"religious headgear\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3038}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic and Paralympic Games\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bans on hijabs are in place across several sports including football, basketball and volleyball, at both professional and amateur levels.\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3231, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bans\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3098}, {\"ngram\": \"hijabs\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3108}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3121}, {\"ngram\": \"several sports\", \"from\": 3129, \"to\": 3143}, {\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 3154, \"to\": 3162}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 3164, \"to\": 3174}, {\"ngram\": \"volleyball\", \"from\": 3179, \"to\": 3189}, {\"ngram\": \"both professional and amateur levels\", \"from\": 3194, \"to\": 3230}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Amnesty International, along with 10 other sports and human rights groups, had earlier appealed to the IOC to intervene on the ban.\", \"from\": 3233, \"to\": 3364, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3233, \"end\": 3254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amnesty_International\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.511111018029464e-15, \"text\": \"Amnesty International\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amnesty_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amnesty_International\"}, {\"begin\": 3336, \"end\": 3339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4275057658665066e